      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIRACLE MAN (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 7 lengths at this track in a handy 23.30. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Looks the one to beat. LEKTRA LEE (2) was strongly fancied last time but ran below expectations when fourth (24.29), beaten 14 lengths. Cannot be taken lightly. ASTON GOSSET (7) showed good speed to score (17.18) off a middle draw two back then off a similar box last time settled off pace and could manage only a 6 length 4th at Murray Bridge Straight (17.20). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Cannot be left out. ULTIMATE (8) can sneak into the finish.",
